      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just \"similar writing style\" though. these posts are using jokes i only tell to my closest friends, and they're bringing up specific things i said in private messages. it's like the AI knows my entire history. i feel like i'm looking at a digital version of myself that's more \"me\" than i am. can't you see how terrifying it is that a machine could just... replace a person's entire identity like that?",
