    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but how can it mimic my language patterns that perfectly if it doesn't have access to everything? if it's using my private jokes and stuff from my DMs, then it basically HAS access. once the AI has enough of your data, there's no actual difference between you and the bot anymore, is there? it's like the digital version has become the real one and i'm just the leftover. don't you think the tech is getting so advanced now that it could actually be happening?",
